# **Ceaseless Skip**

The **Ceaseless Skip** is a **sequence break** that allows the player to skip **Ceaseless Discharge** by rolling through the lava in the **Demon Ruins**. It saves approximately 2:00 minutes.

This skip is **allowed in Glitchless categories**.

## **External Resources**

\
Here is the best tutorial for this skip, covering the entire process. While this older drop method is still viable, it is no longer the most optimal one: [https://youtu.be/ugRKc7A2_9Q](https://youtu.be/ugRKc7A2_9Q) by m3dic on YouTube.

Here is the **fastest method**, featuring a more optimized drop: [https://youtu.be/9l4Bh7d2Ujw](https://youtu.be/9l4Bh7d2Ujw) by m3dic on YouTube.

Finally, here is a video showcasing the **lava deadzones**. Once you decide which drop to use, refer to this for guidance: [https://x.com/i/status/1727408957822771256](https://x.com/i/status/1727408957822771256) by Minitius on Twitter.
